---
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';

// Define all blog post metadata in one place
export const frontmatter = {
  title: "Version 1.1: Introducing Premium Features",
  description: "Introducing version 1.1 of Boxing Timer Champ with new Premium subscription, session logging, ad-free experience, and more improvements.",
  publishDate: '2025-05-12T08:00:00-07:00',
  heroImage: '/images/blog/version-1-1-hero.jpg',
  alt: "Boxing Timer Champ Version 1.1 Update - Premium Features"
};
---

<BlogLayout frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <p class="lead text-xl mb-6">
    We're excited to announce that Boxing Timer Champ version 1.1 is now available on the App Store! This major update introduces our new Premium subscription with exclusive features and several improvements.
  </p>
  
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Introducing Boxing Timer Champ Premium</h2>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    With this update, we're introducing Boxing Timer Champ Premium, an optional upgrade that unlocks session logging history, as well as the ad-free experience.
  </p>
  
  <div class="bg-elegant-secondary p-5 rounded-lg mb-6">
    <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Premium Features Include:</h4>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Ad-Free Experience:</strong> Train without ads during the rest periods</li>
      <li><strong>Session Logging:</strong> Track and analyze completed training sessions</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    The base version of Boxing Timer Champ remains free with all the core timing functionality. Premium is available as one-time upgrade for $9.99 and will include future premium features.
  </p>
  
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What's New in Version 1.1</h2>
  
  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Session Logging (Premium)</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Keep track of your progress with a comprehensive training log:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Complete Session History:</strong> View your past completed training sessions with detailed statistics.</li>
    <li><strong>Progress Tracking:</strong> Monitor your training volume and add notes to your session entries.</li>
    <li><strong>Export Data:</strong> Download your training data as a CSV to use in Google Sheets, Excel, and other tools.</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Enhanced Interval Training</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Interval training options are expanded to give you more control over your workouts:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Precise Timer Fields:</strong> Updated the selections from 15 seconds to 10 to provide greater precision while balancing ease of use.</li>
    <li><strong>Settings Updates:</strong> Overhauled the settings view to make timer customizations even easier.</li>
    <li><strong>Performance Improvements:</strong> Performance improvements to make the app more responsive and reliable.</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3">Coming Soon to Premium</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Here's what to expect with the next set of Premium features:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Apple Watch Support:</strong> Control your timer from your wrist and monitor your heart rate during training</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics Enhancements:</strong> For even more detailed training analysis for your workouts.</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    The core app functionality remains completely free for all users. Premium purchases help continue development and add advanced features.
  </p>
  
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">User Feedback Matters</h2>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    Many of these improvements came directly from your feedback! I'm committed to making Boxing Timer Champ the best boxing training tool, and your input is invaluable.
  </p>
  
  <p class="mb-6">
    If you have any suggestions for future updates or notice any issues, please don't hesitate to reach out through the app or via our website.
  </p>
  
  <div class="my-8 text-center">
    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/boxing-timer-champ/id6744783909" class="inline-block bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg">
      <i class="fab fa-apple mr-2"></i> Update Now
    </a>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
